author: Carianne Luter
title: SnapJAX sunsets: Insiders share stunning sunset photos after severe weather week
text:
As the saying goes: Red sky in the morning, sailors take warning. Red sky at night, sailors delight.
SnapJAX users captured the delight Wednesday and Thursday evening after severe weather blew through Florida and Georgia earlier in the week.
The sky seemed to gift us its beauty after enduring thunderstorms on Tuesday.
